  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the red curry paste and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the fish sauce, palm sugar, coconut milk, bell peppers, chili peppers, and Thai basil. Stir well to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10-15 minutes, until the chicken is cooked through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles."
